  helpText: 'When a pawn exists in the targeted hexes (red) of another pawn, an attack
    happens.


    All attacks happen simultaneously and even if one of the pawns
    would die as a result of an attack.


    Each attacked pawn takes damage equal
    to the formula:

    DMG = max((AttackerATK - DefenderDEF), 1)'
